<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="14Jul1932"><font color="red">14 July 1932</font> <i>NLPK</i> (fromPaul L&eacute;on to J. Ralph Pinker): All during the last three months or more he has been in a terrible state under the influence of his daughter&apos;s health who is suffering from a severe break down &hellip; Mr Joyce is at present in Z&uuml;rich &mdash; Carlton Elite hotel &hellip; The news about Mr Joyce&apos;s eyesight are not comforting lately </div>
